                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The scheme \"Assistance in Trellise Mandap for Cultivation of Vegetable Crops\" by the Agriculture and Co-operation Department, Government of Gujarat, aims to promote sustainable and structured vegetable crop cultivation by extending financial assistance to eligible farmers for building kachha, semi-pucca, and pucca trellis mandaps using materials like wood, bamboo, GI wire, and plastic wire. This initiative not only supports effective vegetable cultivation techniques but also improves the productivity and longevity of vegetable crops grown on trellises. "
